There's so much in this update! Here are some of the highlights:
  • Capture the Conduit - Specific bases have been converted into Conduit Outposts offering new capture mechanics.
  • Enhanced Graphics Features - Enjoy updated sky files and texture refinements as well as expanded options for water and object reflections and anti-aliasing.
  • New Subterfuge Directives - Take part in a variety of devious tasks and missions to reap the rewards.
  • So Much More - Including a revisited spawn system, infantry and vehicle balance updates, Bastion Fleet Carrier changes, A.S.P. Rank 3, and new anniversary bundles in the Depot.

Visit planetside2.com for the full patch notes.
